- Adapt — remix, transform, and build upon the material for any purpose, even commercially.

Under the following terms:
- Attribution — You must give appropriate credit, provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made.
- ShareAlike — If you remix, transform, or build upon the material, you must distribute your contributions under the same license as the original.

Full license text and legal code: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/legalcode

Recommended short notice to add at top of files:
"This repository is licensed under CC BY-SA 4.0 — see LICENSE for details."

Important note about software:
Creative Commons licenses are not ideal for software. If this repository includes software/firmware, consider adding a software-friendly license (MIT/Apache/GPL) for those components while keeping documentation/designs under CC BY-SA. This repository uses MIT for code/firmware and CC BY-SA for docs/designs.
